9. CHILDHOOD. FRIENDS. TO LOVERS

half the time it’s more angst and pining than enemies to lovers. i just think there’s something so wonderful about changing the way you view your best friend and FALLING IN LOVE

8. in character or out of character

hmm i wouldn’t call any of my fics “in character” but i wouldn’t say they’re ooc unless it’s intentional. like lotb. i will say that writing someone extremely ooc without reason feels very off putting

7. rarepairs? yay or nay?

ABSOLUTELY im for the rare pairs. my number one ship is a rare pair. but i’m also a sucker for popular ships too i just like any ship

6. multi-chapter or one shots?

both!! i know that i have a lot of one shots on my page but that’s just because chaptered fics take a really long time. novel fics aren’t easy!!

5. how long do your fics tend to be?

3. third person all the way, i never use first person for fanfiction. sometimes i do for original works, but for the most part i write in third person
